    <item>
      <title>突尼斯总统选举定于 10 月 6 日举行，反对派分裂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/tunisia-sets-oct-6-for-presidential-vote-with-opposition-split</link>
      <description><![CDATA[突尼斯定于 10 月 6 日举行总统选举，这次选举可能成为这个北非国家民主的试金石，该国的民粹主义领导人已经掌握了广泛权力并压制了大多数异议人士。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/tunisia-sets-oct-6-for-presidential-vote-with-opposition-split</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国汽车城希望工党能推动电动汽车电池梦想</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/uk-s-motor-city-hopes-labour-can-jump-start-ev-battery-dream</link>
      <description><![CDATA[考文垂市宣布计划在英格兰西米德兰兹郡的小型机场建造一座巨型电动汽车电池工厂，迄今已过去三年多，这给人们带来了希望，即英国能够赶上在电池生产方面已经领先多年的竞争对手国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/uk-s-motor-city-hopes-labour-can-jump-start-ev-battery-dream</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰合作银行的 Foley 表示，法国僵局不应给市场带来安慰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-gridlock-shouldn-t-comfort-markets-rabobank-s-foley-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰合作银行货币策略师简·福利 (Jane Foley) 表示，周日法国大选后出现悬浮议会的前景不应该让投资者感到高兴，因为这将意味着预算陷入僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-gridlock-shouldn-t-comfort-markets-rabobank-s-foley-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:49:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞寻求多数席位，竞争对手联手阻止她</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-seeks-majority-as-rival-groups-band-together-to-stop-her</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周日举行的法国立法选举最后一轮中，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟正在努力争取绝对多数，而竞争对手则在努力阻止极右翼政党掌权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-seeks-majority-as-rival-groups-band-together-to-stop-her</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:27:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国将向中国申请 50 亿美元贷款以促进经济发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/bangladesh-to-tap-china-for-5-billion-loan-to-bolster-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国央行行长表示，该国正在与中国就一笔约 50 亿美元的贷款进行谈判，以补充该国日益减少的外汇储备，此举拉近了这个南亚国家与北京的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/bangladesh-to-tap-china-for-5-billion-loan-to-bolster-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 05:17:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称正“尽力”帮助老挝减轻债务负担</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/china-says-doing-its-best-to-help-tiny-laos-ease-debt-burden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示正在帮助邻国老挝减轻其沉重的债务负担，此前该东南亚国家透露，其外部还款额已增加近一倍，并希望进一步延期还款以防止违约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/china-says-doing-its-best-to-help-tiny-laos-ease-debt-burden</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 04:56:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芬兰称中国只需一个电话就能结束俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/russia-ukraine-china-can-end-war-with-a-phone-call-finland-s-stubb-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芬兰总统亚历山大·斯塔布称，俄罗斯对中国的依赖已经达到了这样的程度，只要北京愿意，它完全可以结束乌克兰战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/russia-ukraine-china-can-end-war-with-a-phone-call-finland-s-stubb-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍里斯·约翰逊出人意料地采取最后行动，避免保守党被彻底击败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/boris-johnson-makes-surprise-late-move-to-avert-tory-wipeout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鲍里斯·约翰逊 (Boris Johnson) 意外参与了英国大选活动，他敦促保守党选民阻止工党在里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党的最后一搏中取得压倒性胜利，以避免在周四的选举中遭受预计的巨大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/boris-johnson-makes-surprise-late-move-to-avert-tory-wipeout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 21:13:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国扣押台湾渔船或加剧紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-seizes-taiwan-fishing-boat-and-crew-as-tensions-simmer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国扣押了一艘台湾渔船及其船员，此举有可能加剧与台湾新总统的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-seizes-taiwan-fishing-boat-and-crew-as-tensions-simmer</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:25:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国和菲律宾试图缓解海上紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-philippines-hold-talks-after-sea-clash-in-june-rappler</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在两国发生最严重的海上冲突之一之后的会晤中，中国和菲律宾外交官同意缓解南海紧张局势，但坚持各自的主权主张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-philippines-hold-talks-after-sea-clash-in-june-rappler</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 08:48:04 GMT</pubDate>
